<br>
Fury 1 = 2% chance of a 33% crit for a 2/3% increase in average nuke damage.<br>
<br>
Fury 2 = 5% chance of a 66% crit for 3 1/3% increase in average nuke damage.<br>
<br>
Fury 3 = 7% chance of a 100% crit for a 7% increase in average nuke damage.<br>
<br>
Fury 1 provides .333% per AA point spent<br>
Fury 2 provides .555% per AA point spent<br>
Fury 3 provides .583% per AA point spent<br>
<br>
The higher levels provide a larger benefit/point than the lower levels already - your proposal does not correct a diminishing returns situation in the case of Casting Fury, since such a situation does not exist.<br>
<br>
